RETURN OF THE REBELS stars Barbara Eden (VOYAGE TO THE BOTTOM OF THE SEA, THE WOMAN HUNTER, VISIONS OF TERROR) as Mary Beth Allen, owner of a riverside campground business. After being hassled by a group of destructive, young party animals, led by KC (Patrick Swayze!),  Mary Beth begins pining for the days -20 years prior- when she was a biker chick. She looks up some old friends -including Jamie Farr!- and the Eagle Rock Rebels get back together for one more ride, in order to teach KC and his fellow boneheads some manners! As biker movies go, REBELS is very light-hearted and harmless. Don't expect the usual foul language, drugs, or violence. After all, these bikers are the good guys! Is it ridiculous? Of course! Still, it's a fun, silly romp! Besides, I'd watch Ms. Eden in just about anything!...
